verbose_text: While the expression of GATA-3, T-bet and TGF-beta was induced in the muscles followed by an injection of the respective plasmid vectors, the expression of IL-4/13A, IFN-gamma and IL-17A in the muscles, spleen and head kidney was variable and not very well correlated to T-bet, GATA-3 and TGF-beta mRNA levels in the muscles.
evidence: expression of GATA-3, T-bet and TGF-beta
